Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.26,OP BR,,0,0,0,,Despertei na solidão! Solidão!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.56,OP BR,,0,0,0,,Caindo dentro de sua história
